Notes: NCAA Div. III Championship First Round...UWO advances to host Washington Univ.
(Mo.) in the second round on March 8...UWO gets 17 points and nine rebounds
from Stecker...SMU receives 16 points and 17 rebounds from Euerle...UWO scores
eight straight points to take 60-52 lead...Teams opened 8-30 from field.
